headline: Synopsys reports quarterly revenue below estimates, shares fall
summary: (Reuters) -Chip design software provider Synopsys (SNPS) missed Wall Street estimates for third-quarter revenue on Tuesday, hurt by weakness in its Design IP business, sending shares down 20% in premarket trading on Wednesday.
